    "2": {
      "title": "Dark Armor",
      "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Dark_Armor\">Dark Armor</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Skyrim:Dark&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Dark Armor\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:202px;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-item-Dark_Seducer_Armor_Female.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/1/1c/SR-item-Dark_Seducer_Armor_Female.jpg/200px-SR-item-Dark_Seducer_Armor_Female.jpg\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/1/1c/SR-item-Dark_Seducer_Armor_Female.jpg/300px-SR-item-Dark_Seducer_Armor_Female.jpg 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/1/1c/SR-item-Dark_Seducer_Armor_Female.jpg/400px-SR-item-Dark_Seducer_Armor_Female.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-item-Dark_Seducer_Armor_Female.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>A female <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Imperial\" title=\"Skyrim:Imperial\">Imperial</a> wearing Dark Seducer Armor</div></div></div>\n<p>Dark armor is a variety of light armor. When compared to <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Malachite\" title=\"Skyrim:Malachite\">Glass</a>, Dark armor is slightly inferior. In terms of armor rating-to-weight ratio (i.e. the number of armor points per unit of weight), the shield, gauntlets and boots have the highest ratio in the game, with the latter two tying with the <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Elven\" title=\"Skyrim:Elven\">Elven Hunter</a> equivalent.\n</p>\n<table class=\"wikitable sortable striped\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th rowspan=\"2\" class=\"unsortable\">\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\">Name (<a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Form_ID\" title=\"Skyrim:Form ID\">ID</a>)\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_(square).png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Weight\"><img alt=\"Weight\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/22px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/33px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/44px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-item-Gold-heads.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Value\"><img alt=\"Value\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/22px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/33px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/44px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Armor Rating\"><img alt=\"Armor Rating\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/f/f0/SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png/22px-SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/f/f0/SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png/33px-SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/f/f0/SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png/44px-SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\" colspan=\"4\" class=\"unsortable\">Raw Materials\n</th>\n<th style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\" colspan=\"2\" class=\"unsortable\">Delta\n</th>\n<th colspan=\"2\" class=\"unsortable\">Ratio\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-ingot-Ebony_Ingot.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-ingot-Ebony Ingot.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/7/78/SR-icon-ingot-Ebony_Ingot.png/24px-SR-icon-ingot-Ebony_Ingot.png\" width=\"24\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/7/78/SR-icon-ingot-Ebony_Ingot.png/36px-SR-icon-ingot-Ebony_Ingot.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/7/78/SR-icon-ingot-Ebony_Ingot.png/48px-SR-icon-ingot-Ebony_Ingot.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Ebony_Ingot\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Ebony Ingot\">Ebony</a>\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-ingredient-Daedra_Heart.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-ingredient-Daedra Heart.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/b/b1/SR-icon-ingredient-Daedra_Heart.png/24px-SR-icon-ingredient-Daedra_Heart.png\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/b/b1/SR-icon-ingredient-Daedra_Heart.png/36px-SR-icon-ingredient-Daedra_Heart.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/b/b1/SR-icon-ingredient-Daedra_Heart.png/48px-SR-icon-ingredient-Daedra_Heart.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Daedra_Heart\" title=\"Skyrim:Daedra Heart\">Daedra Heart</a>\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-ingot-Quicksilver_Ingot.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-ingot-Quicksilver Ingot.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/c/ce/SR-icon-ingot-Quicksilver_Ingot.png/24px-SR-icon-ingot-Quicksilver_Ingot.png\" width=\"24\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/c/ce/SR-icon-ingot-Quicksilver_Ingot.png/36px-SR-icon-ingot-Quicksilver_Ingot.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/c/ce/SR-icon-ingot-Quicksilver_Ingot.png/48px-SR-icon-ingot-Quicksilver_Ingot.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Quicksilver_Ingot\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Quicksilver Ingot\">Quicksilver</a>\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/3/3a/SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png/24px-SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/3/3a/SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png/36px-SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/3/3a/SR-icon-misc-LeatherStri